\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693c5b99f65137c26a0a28bb35cdcd97ad392c6c","tid":763313,"uid":64405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"Cheer up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4364efafb12f301f8ed4fbc6488bc756a9141002","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係到陪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n多謝你呀，唉點解我會咁眼淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90591261214aa3f0d3d538125644ad2444733b84","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知道唔會做到咩<br />\n自己一個自閉幾日會好好多<br />\n或者幾推薦做運動岀翻身汗<br />\n攰就去休息 <br />\n咁樣日子好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者喺到揾巴絲陪都得嘅<br />\n不過好多仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家日日都做運動，諗住俾段時間自己深切反思同冷靜下，順便麻醉自己，過一段時間再睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7374d383ea7eafad18e9f9a3969217e1320106","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cheer up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f02092d15f320b632b6d18be868fe4e7e5f162","tid":763313,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"有緣千里能相會"},{"pid":"8ca632c8ab430a226fdb2d46cca242d1d72ffb42","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵到錢 你驚無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>啱呀樓主仲咁細<br />\n將來大把貨啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能因為今次初戀嚟，所以對我好大影響<br />\n仲記得嗰日佢話鍾意我，唔知頭唔知路就開始咗。<br />\n其實大家都好夾，傾偈有講有笑。<br />\n雖然開頭拍拖冇咩愛嘅感覺，但係相處落就越係鍾意佢，好想對佢好，關心佢。<br />\n搵到第二個都唔會再係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d411c142b501b38babdfe0c6fef3c96f0983c492","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有緣千里能相會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好好笑<br />\n我地喺網上識<br />\n咁多個入面佢揀到我嚟同佢傾偈<br />\n初頭以為冇乜嘢<br />\n點知有日<br />\n我搭架我同佢都唔係成日搭嘅車嘅時候撞到佢<br />\n我嗰陣真係信緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d6fe1c24ed36948d4c107f48496af75a600253","tid":763313,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"有邊個分手唔辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab597517b83ee684cc773ac87acb2c1bde97a3","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個分手唔辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e28d6202bf1d361877da24a76e16e6eaafcce5","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"啱啱做gym嗰陣<br />\n分分秒秒都諗緊之前同佢拍拖嘅時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083c466d1eada19e1587c3aa9c5e3704addf9def","tid":763313,"uid":194666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e28d6202bf1d361877da24a76e16e6eaafcce5","tid":763313,"uid":196866,"